{"tid":703114,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[好片共賞] 國家地理頻道 揭開北韓的神秘面紗【透視內幕 : 北韓今昔】","createTime":"2018-06-15T12:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T10:32:25.000Z","uid":72478,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99e6247ddd755908da9c364a582fab491e7f1bbe","tid":703114,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:51:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PvAzzLVStGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPvAzzLVStGQ&d=zKocEFSy1qa9rbVPg05Zif755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=13ccec24\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PvAzzLVStGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2006年，國家地理記者凌志慧在眼科手術人道計畫的掩護之下進到北韓，向世人揭露這個封閉、獨裁的社會。在那之後，這個國家經歷諸多改變。領袖金正日過世，他的兒子金正恩掌權。北韓現在已經是核武國家，正在發展能飛抵美國的洲際彈道飛彈。美國前總統歐巴馬曾告訴總統當選人川普，北韓會是他在國際事務上最艱難的任務。新版節目將回顧凌志慧的調查，並更新原有的節目內容。我們也將報導凌志慧的妹妹凌志美的故事。凌志美在擔任潮流電視臺的記者時，越過北韓邊境並遭到逮捕。美國前總統柯林頓出面談判，才讓她和同事獲釋。"},{"pid":"9dcbf32075eba5fd927e28ffc938be7429098da4","tid":703114,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155a8fd13a08f74c012d9ca693ef091c2df91612","tid":703114,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0e45dced38676f55823fe8192270695ece336465","tid":703114,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"155a8fd13a08f74c012d9ca693ef091c2df91612","tid":703114,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9337d66ad7199dfb3d6c9dea3f0c8360e7be5fee","tid":703114,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"正嘢"},{"pid":"3b194560c08881939b2eedb0c4a597b12a218ea3","tid":703114,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9337d66ad7199dfb3d6c9dea3f0c8360e7be5fee","tid":703114,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"正嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好睇"},{"pid":"ff264ddecb1b65f6803d7dabde3eab7b0e33349b","tid":703114,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"有集新野<br />\n【透視北韓：金氏王朝】「北韓於2000年舉辦的離散家屬見面會上，老淚縱橫的父母輕撫著相隔半世紀的兒子臉龐。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DQJ9xxm2byQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDQJ9xxm2byQ&d=zKocEFSy1qa9rbVPg05Zif755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=cedb2811\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DQJ9xxm2byQ</a>"}]}